3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a new ranking method using a rebalance approach, which is a machine learning technique. 
4. cs.SOC (Computational Social Science) - The paper addresses the problem of time bias in ranking, which is a common issue in computational social science. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses classical ranking algorithms and proposes a new method, which is related to data structures and algorithms.
